main event: Vehicle sighting reported with lights seen after dusk in Groveland, Florida.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 25 minutes., The object was tracked on ground-radar and visually., The object had a northwest course., No photographs were taken during the event., The report indicates the possibility of misidentification as a heavenly body.
witness description: One witness, a horticulturist, and the other, a deputy operator from the Florida Forest Service.
